      <li>Reply HELP for assistance.</li>
      <li>Consent is not a condition of purchase.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To opt out of SMS communications, reply STOP to any message or contact us at David@alot.land.</p>

    <h2>5. Accuracy of Information</h2>
    <p>We make reasonable efforts to ensure property listings and information on this Site are accurate and up to date. However, we make no warranties regarding the completeness, accuracy, or timeliness of any information. Property availability and pricing are subject to change without notice.</p>

